GO FARTHER, STARTING WITH 20,000 FLEXPOINTS
Earn 20,000 bonus FlexPoints® after you spend $1,500 in purchases within 3 months of account opening - redeemable for $200 in gift cards.
 
Redeem FlexPoints for almost anything, from a large selection of gift cards including dining, entertainment and retail – to an amazing selection of valuable rewards such as electronics, travel rewards, home goods, books and media, charitable donations or even cash.
EARN FLEXPOINTS QUICKLY
• Points do not expire and earn unlimited FlexPoints
• Double FlexPoints per dollar spent on purchases for dining at restaurants and entertainment
• One FlexPoint per $1 spent on other purchases
• Exclusive events for FlexPoints Cardmembers
SERVICES
Personal Concierge Service
Have the knowledge of a local at your fingertips, no matter where you are. With Flex Personal Concierge Service, you’ll always know the best places to stay and eat, where to shop and how to get around.
 
Manage Your Account Online and On The Go
Enjoy 24/7 access to your account online. Check your balance, view transactions, and even make a payment using free online and mobile banking tools. Get free accounts alerts delivered right on your mobile device.
 
Choose your Payment Due Date
Choose to pay your bill on any available due date in the beginning, middle or end of the month. Enjoy the flexibility of paying your full balance or just the minimum payment due each month.
 
Additional Cards
Getting additional cards is easy. Just call the number on the back of your credit card. Please allow 3 weeks to process your request.
 
Extended Warranty
Extends the manufacturer's original U.S. warranty (of one year or less) up to one additional year on most items purchased with your Credit card.

REWARDS
• EARN 5% CASH BACK every quarter in must have categories. Right now, on eligible purchases within the Hilton portfolio, car rental agencies, movie theaters and theme parks from July 1, 2014, to September 30, 2014. Enrollment each quarter is quick and easy.
• Full 1% cash back on purchases and on cash advances taken at the standard cash advance rate
• 5% unlimited cash back on average when you shop at over 400 leading retailers with the Flex Bonus Cash Center®
• $5 cash back on individual balance transfer transactions of $1500 or more
